### COMPILED QUERY TEST - PaymentService
### Test các compiled queries với Marten

### ============================================
### BƯỚC 1: Tạo dữ liệu test (nếu chưa có)
### ============================================

### 1.1 Tạo account đầu tiên
POST http://localhost:5160/api/account
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "policyNumber": "POL001",
    "policyAccountNumber": "ACC001",
    "ownerName": "Nguyen Van A",
    "balance": 1500.50
}

### 1.2 Tạo account thứ hai
POST http://localhost:5160/api/account
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "policyNumber": "POL002",
    "policyAccountNumber": "ACC002",
    "ownerName": "Tran Thi B",
    "balance": 6000.75
}

### 1.3 Tạo account thứ ba
POST http://localhost:5160/api/account
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "policyNumber": "POL003",
    "policyAccountNumber": "ACC003",
    "ownerName": "Nguyen Van C",
    "balance": 2500.25
}

### ============================================
### BƯỚC 2: TEST COMPILED QUERIES
### ============================================

### 2.1 Find by PolicyNumber (Compiled)
GET http://localhost:5160/api/compiled/policy/POL001

### 2.2 Find by OwnerName (Compiled)
GET http://localhost:5160/api/compiled/owner/Nguyen Van A

### 2.3 Find balance greater than (Compiled)
GET http://localhost:5160/api/compiled/balance/greater-than/2000

### 2.4 Find balance in range (Compiled)
GET http://localhost:5160/api/compiled/balance/range/1000/5000

### 2.5 Search owner name contains (Compiled)
GET http://localhost:5160/api/compiled/search/owner/Nguyen

### 2.6 Find by account number (Compiled)
GET http://localhost:5160/api/compiled/account-number/ACC002

### 2.7 Count by owner (Compiled)
GET http://localhost:5160/api/compiled/count/owner/Nguyen Van A

### 2.8 Sum balance by owner (Compiled)
GET http://localhost:5160/api/compiled/sum-balance/owner/Nguyen Van A

### 2.9 Get top accounts (Compiled)
GET http://localhost:5160/api/compiled/top/3

### 2.10 Get all ordered by balance (Compiled)
GET http://localhost:5160/api/compiled/all-ordered

### 2.11 Get paged results (Compiled)
GET http://localhost:5160/api/compiled/paged/1/2

